@Comment:	Time is 0:06
@Comment:	hard to tell Chi and FRI apart. Fat , Chi and FRI are very into sports and are watching a hockey game during the meal; the affect among family members is not very pleasant; it's as if everyone makes a point of not caring about everyone else's business; or at least they're not very polite-Chi says <look Dad I don't want any lip> at one point; talk about Chi's ice hockey team; most of the talk is among Chi , FRI , and Bro; mealtime is about 15 minutes long;
@Comment:	I suspect that FRI may actually be a cousin or something but there is no specific mentioning of cousins visiting in HV3 or HV4 interview , although either Mot's or Fat's sister is in the area
